text: Kentucky Route 137 (KY 137) is a state highway in Livingston County, Kentucky. It runs from U.S. Route 60 (US 60) north of Smithfield to KY 133 in rural Livingston County south of Carrsville. KY 137 is split into two segments by a gap on the northwest side of Carrsville. ==Major intersections== ==References== 0137 Category:Transportation in Livingston County, Kentucky
